ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great.Students with an interest in international economics and country economics should definitely take this course.
This should be a mandatory course for all IR students, taken immediately after microeconomics. Very important concepts for understanding pressures highly significant to state actions.
i would recommend it to someone interested in applied macro
Yes. This course uses current real-world examples of macroeconomic situations.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Definitely helped. I learnt a lot about different countries and how macroeconomic policies play out in the real world.Case studies done in class were very insightful. Absolutely love the class discussions and reference materials provided by the professor.
